The paper discusses a blockchain-based, decentralized data marketplace that focuses on secure and anonymous data exchange. This topic is closely related to computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions financial incentives and payment processing, which could fall under cybernetics (cs.CY) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the use of smart contracts and blockchain technology could also relate to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
